summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Milwaukee Land Company, an Iowa corporation, to certain lands in Sections Eight (8) and Eighteen (18) in Township Twenty-two (22) North, Range Eight (8) East, W. M., all in Cedar River Watershed, King County, Washington, and appropriating Four Hundred Fifty-eight and Ninety-eight Hundredths ($458.98) Dollars from Cedar River Watershed Condemnation Fund in payment of said lands.
